devdoc.details: This contract is for testing purposes only.

completeFactoryUpgrade().details: It is the second part of the two-step factory upgrade process. The function can be called after factory upgrade time delay period has passed since the new factory upgrade. It emits an event containing the new factory address.

params.factory: Keep factory contract registered initially in the vendor contract.
params.registryAddress: Keep registry contract linked to this contract.

upgradeFactory(address).details: Registers a new ECDSA keep factory. Address cannot be zero and cannot be the same that is currently registered. It is a first part of the two-step factory upgrade process. The function emits an event containing the new factory address and current block timestamp.

devdoc.title: Bonded ECDSA Keep Vendor Implementation Stub

initialized().notice: Checks if this contract is initialized.

selectFactory().notice: Selects the latest ECDSA keep factory.

upgradeFactory(address).notice: Starts new ECDSA keep factory upgrade.
